    Create a website containing Header, Navigation, Main and Footer. The Main section should include a container and
four divs which each contain minimum of one picture and one div that includes text. Start with the mobile first approach and
organize the content of the first div using display:inline-block, the second using position:absolute, the third using floats and
the fourth using flexbox. Add a couple of extra pictures to the fourth div.
The container can be organized using the method that you want to. 
You can design and complete Header and Footer as you please,
but Navigation should include links to each div in the Main section.Finally make a tablet and a display versio of the page. -->
